# SOLID design principles

Follow the canonical standard:

- SOLID design principles → [`agent-standards/15-solid-design.md`](../../agent-standards/15-solid-design.md)

Summary: Single Responsibility (one reason to change); Open/Closed (extend, don't modify);
Liskov Substitution (subtypes honor contracts); Interface Segregation (small, focused interfaces);
Dependency Inversion (depend on abstractions, inject dependencies). Apply judiciously — add an
abstraction for a real need, not speculatively.
